  "description": "The image depicts a lush, moss-covered forest floor dotted with numerous rounded rocks and boulders. Sunlight filters through the dense canopy of tall trees, creating dappled lighting and casting long shadows. The rocks are almost entirely obscured by vibrant green moss, giving the scene a soft, velvety texture. Small ferns and other low-growing vegetation sprout amidst the rocks and fallen leaves. The forest appears dense and somewhat overgrown, hinting at a humid and thriving ecosystem. The overall composition is natural and wild, emphasizing the beauty of the undisturbed woodland.",
